    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Multi-Fidelity Aerodynamic Shape Optimization of a BWB Aircraft</h1>\n<p>Designed an <strong>automated multi-fidelity aerodynamic optimization framework</strong> for a Long Range Blended Wing Body (BWB) aircraft.</p>\n<p>✔ <strong>75.95% drag reduction</strong><br>\n✔ <strong>38.96% MTOW reduction</strong><br>\n✔ <strong>35.96% fuel efficiency improvement</strong><br>\n✔ <strong>8000 NM mission-level validation</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6e274797171111272b67bdb1d179ccd0/15f58/initial.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.14285714285714%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Initial BWB Geometry\"\n        title=\"Initial BWB Geometry\"\n        src=\"/static/6e274797171111272b67bdb1d179ccd0/39600/initial.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6e274797171111272b67bdb1d179ccd0/1aaec/initial.png 175w,\n/static/6e274797171111272b67bdb1d179ccd0/98287/initial.png 350w,\n/static/6e274797171111272b67bdb1d179ccd0/39600/initial.png 700w,\n/static/6e274797171111272b67bdb1d179ccd0/57cd1/initial.png 1050w,\n/static/6e274797171111272b67bdb1d179ccd0/4af54/initial.png 1400w,\n/static/6e274797171111272b67bdb1d179ccd0/15f58/initial.png 2366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><em>Figure 1: Baseline geometry of the Long Range BWB aircraft</em></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Project Overview</h2>\n<p>Traditional low-fidelity mission analysis tools struggle to capture <strong>transonic aerodynamic effects</strong> such as shock formation and compressibility drag.</p>\n<p>This project bridges conceptual aircraft design and <strong>high-fidelity CFD-based optimization</strong>, enabling faster iteration with improved aerodynamic accuracy.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Multi-Fidelity Toolchain</h2>\n<p>The automated workflow integrates multiple engineering tools:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>SUAVE</strong> → mission sizing, fuel burn, and performance analysis</li>\n<li><strong>OpenVSP</strong> → parametric geometry generation</li>\n<li><strong>GMSH</strong> → mesh generation</li>\n<li><strong>SU2</strong> → high-fidelity RANS CFD simulation</li>\n<li><strong>Python</strong> → workflow automation and optimization control</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7517c7ebe1ff00b082609cf2de3fdf31/f3914/tool.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.142857142857146%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Optimization Workflow\"\n        title=\"Optimization Workflow\"\n        src=\"/static/7517c7ebe1ff00b082609cf2de3fdf31/39600/tool.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7517c7ebe1ff00b082609cf2de3fdf31/1aaec/tool.png 175w,\n/static/7517c7ebe1ff00b082609cf2de3fdf31/98287/tool.png 350w,\n/static/7517c7ebe1ff00b082609cf2de3fdf31/39600/tool.png 700w,\n/static/7517c7ebe1ff00b082609cf2de3fdf31/57cd1/tool.png 1050w,\n/static/7517c7ebe1ff00b082609cf2de3fdf31/4af54/tool.png 1400w,\n/static/7517c7ebe1ff00b082609cf2de3fdf31/f3914/tool.png 2314w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><em>Figure 2: Automated multi-fidelity optimization workflow</em></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Geometry Parameterization</h2>\n<p>Implemented <strong>Free Form Deformation (FFD)</strong> to enable global aircraft shape morphing without manual remodeling.</p>\n<p>This allowed optimization of:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Wing twist</li>\n<li>Airfoil variation</li>\n<li>Leading/trailing edge deformation</li>\n<li>Fuselage-wing blending</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2ef134ecb7ba73c11cd862348e7dd2dd/3d868/ffd.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"FFD Geometry\"\n        title=\"FFD Geometry\"\n        src=\"/static/2ef134ecb7ba73c11cd862348e7dd2dd/39600/ffd.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2ef134ecb7ba73c11cd862348e7dd2dd/1aaec/ffd.png 175w,\n/static/2ef134ecb7ba73c11cd862348e7dd2dd/98287/ffd.png 350w,\n/static/2ef134ecb7ba73c11cd862348e7dd2dd/39600/ffd.png 700w,\n/static/2ef134ecb7ba73c11cd862348e7dd2dd/57cd1/ffd.png 1050w,\n/static/2ef134ecb7ba73c11cd862348e7dd2dd/4af54/ffd.png 1400w,\n/static/2ef134ecb7ba73c11cd862348e7dd2dd/3d868/ffd.png 2442w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><em>Figure 3: FFD lattice used for geometry control</em></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Performance Improvements</h2>\n<p>The optimized design significantly reduced aerodynamic drag and improved mission-level efficiency.</p>\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto; margin: 3em 0;\">\n  <table style=\"width: 100%; table-layout: fixed; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.95em;\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: var(--light-navy); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--green);\">\n        <th style=\"width: 60%; text-align: left; padding: 20px; color: var(--lightest-slate);\">Metric</th>\n        <th style=\"width: 40%; text-align: right; padding: 20px; color: var(--lightest-slate);\">Improvement</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--lightest-navy);\">\n        <td style=\"text-align: left; padding: 20px;\">Total Drag Coefficient</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: right; padding: 20px; font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--green);\"><strong>-75.95%</strong></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid var(--lightest-navy);\">\n        <td style=\"text-align: left; padding: 20px;\">Maximum Take-Off Weight</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: right; padding: 20px; font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--green);\"><strong>-38.96%</strong></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"text-align: left; padding: 20px;\">Fuel Efficiency</td>\n        <td style=\"text-align: right; padding: 20px; font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--green);\"><strong>+35.96%</strong></td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/54abc551d0b084e81679062b318f242b/89856/p1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.714285714285715%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Pressure Distribution\"\n        title=\"Pressure Distribution\"\n        src=\"/static/54abc551d0b084e81679062b318f242b/39600/p1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/54abc551d0b084e81679062b318f242b/1aaec/p1.png 175w,\n/static/54abc551d0b084e81679062b318f242b/98287/p1.png 350w,\n/static/54abc551d0b084e81679062b318f242b/39600/p1.png 700w,\n/static/54abc551d0b084e81679062b318f242b/57cd1/p1.png 1050w,\n/static/54abc551d0b084e81679062b318f242b/4af54/p1.png 1400w,\n/static/54abc551d0b084e81679062b318f242b/89856/p1.png 1790w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><em>Figure 4: Optimized pressure distribution across the airframe</em></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/87cc130d58174359f08e7ad1d7aa1e80/94392/p2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 60%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Pressure Coefficient Comparison\"\n        title=\"Pressure Coefficient Comparison\"\n        src=\"/static/87cc130d58174359f08e7ad1d7aa1e80/39600/p2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/87cc130d58174359f08e7ad1d7aa1e80/1aaec/p2.png 175w,\n/static/87cc130d58174359f08e7ad1d7aa1e80/98287/p2.png 350w,\n/static/87cc130d58174359f08e7ad1d7aa1e80/39600/p2.png 700w,\n/static/87cc130d58174359f08e7ad1d7aa1e80/57cd1/p2.png 1050w,\n/static/87cc130d58174359f08e7ad1d7aa1e80/4af54/p2.png 1400w,\n/static/87cc130d58174359f08e7ad1d7aa1e80/94392/p2.png 1618w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><em>Figure 5: Pressure coefficient comparison across spanwise sections</em></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Mission-Level Validation</h2>\n<p>The optimized aircraft was evaluated over an <strong>8000 NM mission profile</strong>.</p>\n<p>Results showed:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Lower compressibility drag</li>\n<li>Better lift-to-drag ratio</li>\n<li>Improved cruise efficiency</li>\n<li>Lower fuel consumption</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1366138011e57b3b98a827ecabd10891/f9e14/mission.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 65.71428571428571%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Mission Analysis\"\n        title=\"Mission Analysis\"\n        src=\"/static/1366138011e57b3b98a827ecabd10891/39600/mission.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1366138011e57b3b98a827ecabd10891/1aaec/mission.png 175w,\n/static/1366138011e57b3b98a827ecabd10891/98287/mission.png 350w,\n/static/1366138011e57b3b98a827ecabd10891/39600/mission.png 700w,\n/static/1366138011e57b3b98a827ecabd10891/57cd1/mission.png 1050w,\n/static/1366138011e57b3b98a827ecabd10891/4af54/mission.png 1400w,\n/static/1366138011e57b3b98a827ecabd10891/f9e14/mission.png 2308w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><em>Figure 6: Mission performance comparison across full range</em></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Key Takeaway</h2>\n<p>This project demonstrates how <strong>multi-fidelity optimization workflows</strong> can combine rapid conceptual design with high-fidelity aerodynamic precision to achieve substantial performance gains in next-generation aircraft design.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Multi-Fidelity Aerodynamic Shape Optimization of a BWB Aircraft","description":"Built an automated multi-fidelity optimization framework for a Long Range Blended Wing Body aircraft, achieving a 76% reduction in total drag.","date":"2020-04-01","slug":"/featured/bwb-optimization","tags":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/featured/bwb-optimization"}},
